OL,3,CDramatic 13 hour rescue sees yacht
OL,4,Ccrew facing 'risk to life'
OL,6,FLifeboat volunteers in Cornwall
OL,7,Fcarried out a dramatic 13 hour rescue
OL,8,Fafter a yacht lost steering and the
OL,9,Fcrew onboard was put in a life-
OL,10,Fthreatening situation.
OL,12,FThe RNLI was first alerted to reports
OL,13,Fthat a yacht had lost control of its
OL,14,Fsteering 40 nautical miles off the
OL,15,Fcoast of the Lizard by the Falmouth
OL,16,FCoastguard at 10:30am on Monday 15
OL,17,FJuly.
