OL,3,CDramatic 13 hour rescue sees yacht
OL,4,Ccrew facing 'risk to life'
OL,6,FThe Coxswain and his six volunteers
OL,7,Fdecided to call for assistance,
OL,8,Fleading to the Penlee Lifeboat joining
OL,9,Fthem at 3pm.
OL,11,FTheir all-weather Severn Class
OL,12,Flifeboat, the Ivan Ellen, arrived two
OL,13,Fhours later and took over the tow,
OL,14,Fwhile the Lizard's Rose acted as a
OL,15,Fbrake behind the yacht.
OL,17,FThe tow itself then lasted for several
OL,18,Fhours with both lifeboats and the
OL,19,Fyacht arriving into Newlyn some 13
OL,20,Fhours after the Lizard crew first set
OL,21,Foff for the rescue.
